high_descs: Turn around and face the counter where the alarm clock is behind you.
Grab the bowl that is on the counter where the alarm clock is.
With the bowl in hand go to the desk
Place the bowl to the right of the phone that is on the desk.
Turn around and go to the shelf that is to the left of the boots.
Grab the bowl that is on the bottom shelf.
With the bowl in hand turn and go to the desk.
Place the bowl to the left of the phone that is on the desk.
Turn around to the shelf next to the desk.
Pick up the bowl on the shelf.
Turn to the desk on the right.
Set the bowl on the desk to the right of the laptop.
Turn around and go to the long shelf on the right.
Pick up the bowl on the bottom shelf.
Turn and go past the shelf on the left to the desk.
Set the bowl down on the left side of the laptop.
anns.task_desc: Set two bowls on the desk.

high_descs: Turn around and face the table built into the wall.
Pick up the bowl on the table in the wall.
Turn to the right to face the white table.
Place the bowl on the white table to the right of the lap top.
Turn around and walk halfway across the room, then turn right and face the left end of the shelves.
Pick up the bowl on the bottom shelf.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the white table.
Place the bowl on the left side of the lap top.
anns.task_desc: To gather two bowls in a room and place one on each side of the lap top on the white table.
